sentences: Yip is also the owner of Memory Music, an independent record label he launched in June, 2015, featuring projects worked on at Studio 4.
On October 8, 2013, Yip released a compilation entitled Off The Board: A Studio 4 Compilation.
In early 2017,  Yip alongside Atlantic Records launched the imprint, "Black Cement Records", with the first release being Tigers Jaw's, Spin.
